race.description: John Watts Memorial Country Boosted Mdn Plate
race.comment: INCY VINCY (8) debuts for the Cavanough yard and looked much sharper in her second trial here, finding the line with purpose. The booking of Bell is a strong push and she can strike first-up. VARAZZE (5) continues to chase a maiden win but went close at Tuncurry two back. Forgive the latest effort, he's fit and finds a thin race. Big chance. NULKABA STAR (3) hinted at ability last prep but struggled to finish off. Untested at the trials this time but could show up fresh in this company. YES YES BOSS (6) has speed but fades late. The drop in trip might be the key. DAME SCHWARZKOPF (7) resumes and looks best of the rest.
